OL,3,CBirmingham bin driver forced out of
OL,4,Cjob weeks before Christmas
OL,6,FAfter spending the last decade
OL,7,Fcollecting Birmingham's bins, George
OL,8,FWilson never imagined his job would
OL,9,Fend this way.
OL,11,FThe 60-year-old has become the first
OL,12,Fbin lorry driver to be compulsorily
OL,13,Fmade redundant, as part of the city's
OL,14,Flong-running refuse dispute.
OL,16,FHe says he refused to accept a pay cut
OL,17,Fof around #7,000, something the
OL,18,Fcouncil disputes.
