OL,3,CBirmingham bin driver forced out of
OL,4,Cjob weeks before Christmas
OL,6,FGeorge says he now faces an uncertain
OL,7,Ffuture with his family's Christmas now
OL,8,Fbeing scaled back.
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council said nobody
OL,11,Fhad to lose out as a result of its
OL,12,Fchanges to the service.
OL,14,FGeorge, who has worked as a full-time
OL,15,Fdriver since 2015, had expected to
OL,16,Fremain in the job until retirement.
OL,18,F"I didn't want to leave. It was a
OL,19,Freally good job."
