OL,6,FGeorge is one of three refuse workers
OL,7,Fwho have now been made compulsorily
OL,8,Fredundant, although around 80 others
OL,9,Fare thought to have accepted voluntary
OL,10,Fredundancy since the dispute began.
OL,12,FHe said the council offered him
OL,13,Fseveral alternatives, including moving
OL,14,Fto a lower Grade 3 role, which would
OL,15,Fhave meant a significant pay cut,
OL,16,Ftaking voluntary redundancy, or
OL,17,Fapplying for a lateral Grade 4 post
OL,18,Felsewhere within the authority.
