OL,6,F"They said the jobs would be available
OL,7,Ffor us to move over, but that wasn't
OL,8,Ftrue," he said.
OL,10,F"There were 12 jobs for 130 drivers,
OL,11,Fand eight of those were already taken."
OL,13,FAfter rejecting the options, George
OL,14,Fwas told he would be "dismissed by
OL,15,Freason of redundancy."
OL,17,FITV News Central has contacted the
OL,18,FCity Council for a response.
