OL,6,FGeorge will receive statutory
OL,7,Fredundancy pay of several thousand
OL,8,Fpounds, but says it will not be enough
OL,9,Fto support him through to retirement.
OL,11,FFor striking workers across the city,
OL,12,Fthe financial strain is growing.
OL,14,FBin workers are currently receiving
OL,15,Funion strike pay of about #80 a day,
OL,16,Fwith many saying they have had to cut
OL,17,Fback on spending in the run-up to
OL,18,FChristmas.
