OL,6,FOne striking worker told ITV News
OL,7,FCentral: "The kids are going to be
OL,8,Fasking questions and wondering why
OL,9,FChristmas is different this year."
OL,11,FAnother said, "We are having to cut
OL,12,Fback on stuff, though no fault of our
OL,13,Fown."
OL,15,FThe dispute has escalated in recent
OL,16,Fweeks, with agency refuse workers
OL,17,Fjoining council staff on strike.
OL,19,FUnite claims support for the strike is
OL,20,Fincreasing and has accused the council
OL,21,Fof mishandling the dispute.
