OL,3,CBirmingham bin driver forced out of
OL,4,Cjob weeks before Christmas
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has rejected
OL,7,Fallegations of bullying and
OL,8,Fblacklisting within its refuse
OL,9,Fdepartment, describing the claims as
OL,10,Funfounded, and said an investigation
OL,11,Ffound no evidence of wrongdoing.
OL,13,FThe council said changes to the refuse
OL,14,Fservice were necessary to modernise
OL,15,Foperations and deal with financial
OL,16,Fpressures, adding that it remained
OL,17,Fopen to discussions.
OL,19,FWhile talks continue, George says the
OL,20,Foutcome for him is already settled.
